title.rendered: TTE moved to its new headquarters

content.rendered: TTE recently moved into the new headquarters located on the busy Al Ittihad Road, with a view of the runways of the Dubai International Airport. With employee health and wellbeing as the focal point of its design, construction, and operations, TTE has capitalized on the strength of the ESAG Group, where eleven sister entities have collaborated on the project with over 250 brands installed on the premises.
